{"id":145,"parent_id":141,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":145,"title":"1 Corinthians 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Christ’s ministers must be faithful—The Apostles suffer, minister, and keep the faith—The kingdom of God is not in word but in power."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.1","order":"03.09.004.17031"},["b","1"],"Let a man so account of us, as of the ministers of Christ, and stewards of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"mysteries"],"of God."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.2","order":"03.09.004.17032"},["b","2"],"Moreover it is required in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"stewards"],", that a man be found",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"faithful"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.3","order":"03.09.004.17033"},["b","3"],"But with me it is a very small thing that I should be judged of you, or of man’s judgment: yea, I judge not mine own self."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.4","order":"03.09.004.17034"},["b","4"],"For I know nothing",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"by myself"],"; yet am I not hereby justified: but he that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"judgeth"],"me is the Lord."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.5","order":"03.09.004.17035"},["b","5"],"Therefore judge nothing before the time, until the Lord come, who both will bring to light the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"hidden things"],"of darkness, and will make",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"manifest"],"the counsels of the hearts: and then shall every man have praise of God."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.6","order":"03.09.004.17036"},["b","6"],"And these things, brethren, I have in a figure transferred to myself and",["i","to"],"Apollos for your sakes; that ye might learn in us not to think",["i","of men"],"above that which is written, that no one of you be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"puffed up for"],"one against another."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.7","order":"03.09.004.17037"},["b","7"],"For who maketh thee",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"to differ",["i","from"]],["i","another"],["i","?"],"and what hast thou that thou didst not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"receive"],"? now if thou didst receive",["i","it,"],"why dost thou glory, as if thou hadst not received",["i","it?"]],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.8","order":"03.09.004.17038"},["b","8"],"Now ye are full, now ye are rich, ye have reigned as kings without us: and I would to God ye did reign, that we also might reign with you."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.9","order":"03.09.004.17039"},["b","9"],"For I think that God hath set forth us the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"apostles last"],", as it were",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"appointed"],"to death: for we are made a spectacle unto the world, and to angels, and to men."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.10","order":"03.09.004.17040"},["b","10"],"We",["i","are"],"fools for Christ’s sake, but ye",["i","are"],"wise in Christ; we",["i","are"],"weak, but ye",["i","are"],"strong; ye",["i","are"],"honourable, but we",["i","are"],"despised."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.11","order":"03.09.004.17041"},["b","11"],"Even unto this present hour we both hunger, and thirst, and are naked, and are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"buffeted"],", and have no certain dwellingplace;"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.12","order":"03.09.004.17042"},["b","12"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"labour"],", working with our",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"own"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"hands"],": being",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_12d"},"reviled"],", we bless; being",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_12e"},"persecuted"],", we",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_12f"},"suffer it"],":"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.13","order":"03.09.004.17043"},["b","13"],"Being defamed, we entreat: we are made as the filth of the world,",["i","and are"],"the offscouring of all things unto this day."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.14","order":"03.09.004.17044"},["b","14"],"I write not these things to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"shame"],"you, but as my beloved",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"sons"],"I",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"warn"],["i","you."]],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.15","order":"03.09.004.17045"},["b","15"],"For though ye have ten thousand instructors in Christ, yet",["i","have ye"],"not many fathers: for in Christ Jesus I have begotten you through the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.16","order":"03.09.004.17046"},["b","16"],"Wherefore I beseech you, be ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"followers"],"of me."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.17","order":"03.09.004.17047"},["b","17"],"For this cause have I sent unto you",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Timotheus"],", who is my beloved son, and faithful in the Lord, who shall bring you into remembrance of my ways which be in Christ, as I teach every where in every church."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.18","order":"03.09.004.17048"},["b","18"],"Now some are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"puffed up"],", as though I would not come to you."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.19","order":"03.09.004.17049"},["b","19"],"But I will come to you shortly, if the Lord will, and will know, not the speech of them which are puffed up, but the power."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.20","order":"03.09.004.17050"},["b","20"],"For the kingdom of God",["i","is"],"not in word, but in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"power"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.21","order":"03.09.004.17051"},["b","21"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"What will ye"],"? shall I come unto you with a rod, or in love, and",["i","in"],"the spirit of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"meekness"],"?"]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.1a","order":"03.09.004.17052"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-knowledge-about"},"TG God, Knowledge about"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mysteries-of-godliness"},"Mysteries of Godliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.2a","order":"03.09.004.17054"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/delegation-of-responsibility"},"TG Delegation of Responsibility"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stewardship"},"Stewardship"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.2b","order":"03.09.004.17056"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/trustworthiness"},"TG Trustworthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.4a","order":"03.09.004.17058"},["b","4a"],["span.small","JST"],"1 Cor. 4:4 …",["i","against"],"myself …"],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.4b","order":"03.09.004.17060"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.5a","order":"03.09.004.17062"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.13"},"D&C 123:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.5b","order":"03.09.004.17064"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/2.16"},"Rom. 2:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.6a","order":"03.09.004.17066"},["b","6a"],["span.small","GR"],"proud, arrogant.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.24"},"D&C 38:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.7a","order":"03.09.004.17068"},["b","7a"],["span.small","GR"],"different from, superior to."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.7b","order":"03.09.004.17070"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.19"},"Mosiah 4:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.9a","order":"03.09.004.17072"},["b","9a"],["span.small","GR"],"last apostles.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/1.1"},"Rom. 1:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/11.34.33-34"},"1 Ne. 11:34 (33–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.9b","order":"03.09.004.17074"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.48"},"D&C 42:48"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.11a","order":"03.09.004.17076"},["b","11a"],["span.small","GR"],"roughly treated, afflicted."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.12a","order":"03.09.004.17078"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/labor"},"TG Labor"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.12b","order":"03.09.004.17080"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-sacrifice"},"TG Self-Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.12c","order":"03.09.004.17082"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.40"},"D&C 38:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"12d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.12d","order":"03.09.004.17084"},["b","12d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/malice"},"TG Malice"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reviling"},"Reviling"],"."],["div",{"id":"12e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.12e","order":"03.09.004.17086"},["b","12e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/persecution"},"TG Persecution"],"."],["div",{"id":"12f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.12f","order":"03.09.004.17088"},["b","12f"],["span.small","GR"],"endure patiently."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.14a","order":"03.09.004.17090"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shame"},"TG Shame"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.14b","order":"03.09.004.17092"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.11"},"1 Thes. 2:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.14c","order":"03.09.004.17094"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/warn"},"TG Warn"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.15a","order":"03.09.004.17096"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gospel"},"TG Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.16a","order":"03.09.004.17098"},["b","16a"],["span.small","GR"],"imitators.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/11.1"},"1 Cor. 11:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.17a","order":"03.09.004.17100"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/16.1"},"Acts 16:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/1.2"},"1 Tim. 1:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.18a","order":"03.09.004.17102"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"},"TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.20a","order":"03.09.004.17104"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/1.18.17-18"},"1 Cor. 1:18 (17–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.47"},"D&C 18:47"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.14"},"42:14"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-power-of"},"TG Priesthood, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.21a","order":"03.09.004.17106"},["b","21a"],["span.small","IE"],"Which do you choose?"],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.21b","order":"03.09.004.17108"},["b","21b"],["span.small","GR"],"gentleness, kindness."]]}
